# 👋 Hi, I'm Abhishek Atole

I'm a passionate software developer focused on C++, system-level programming, and back-end logic. I enjoy building efficient, low-level systems and solving complex problems with clean and maintainable code. I'm actively seeking roles as a **C++ Developer**, **System Engineer**, or **Backend Engineer** where I can contribute to impactful projects and grow my technical depth.

---

## 💼 Technical Skills

- 💻 **Languages**: C, C++, Java, Python, Bash
- 🧠 **Core Concepts**: Data Structures & Algorithms, File Systems, Memory Management, OS Internals, Networking Basics
- 📦 **Libraries/Frameworks**: CGAL, Qt, STL, OpenMP, TensorFlow (basic), Matplotlib
- 🖥️ **Tools & Systems**: Linux, Git, Docker, CMake, GDB, GCC/Clang, Make, VS Code
- 🧪 **Practices**: OOP, Template Programming, CLI Tools, Version Control, Debugging, Performance Profiling

---

## 🚀 Projects

🔹 [**Polygon Boolean Operations Visualizer**](https://github.com/Abhishek-Atole/Polygon_Boolean_Operations_Visualizer)  
> A Qt + CGAL-based C++ desktop app to visualize union, intersection, and other Boolean operations on polygons.

🔹 [**Customised Virtual File System**](https://github.com/Abhishek-Atole/Customised-Virtual-File-System-)  
> A simulation of a Unix-like file system in C, demonstrating OS-level structures like inodes and file descriptors.

🔹 [**Generalised Data Structures Library**](https://github.com/Abhishek-Atole/Generalised-Data-Structures-Library-)  
> A reusable C++ library of linear and non-linear data structures designed with OOP and template programming.

🔹 [**EMG Signal Classification Using CNN**](https://github.com/Abhishek-Atole/Classification-of-an-EMG-Signal-Using-CNN)  
> A deep learning project to classify electromyography signals using CNN and signal processing techniques.

